SUMMARY:Lessons in innovation: behind the scenes of tech success
DESCRIPTION:Innovation fuels progress. This session will look at the “magic sauce” behind successful tech projects. We’ll look at what drives innovation: user needs\, emerging technologies\, fails\, and a sprinkle of creative disruption. We’ll also think about what we can do to encourage a culture that embraces calculated risks\, and celebrates the rewards of pushing boundaries\, explore ideas for staying ahead of the curve by identifying the next cutting-edge advancements (surviving the current ones!) and fostering a psychologically safe environment where groundbreaking ideas can take off.\n\n\n
CATEGORIES:15-MINUTE PRESENTATION (+5 MINUTE Q&A)
